item.title: O_ops: It's Christmas Time
item.description: I had been wondering for a last couple of days if I should start a O_ops series to just list downs things that are O_ops. Then I get this email and here I start! It was Christmas time and I got an unusual wish from a sweetheart friend of mine. From: SS Sent: Friday, December 24, 2010 5:37 PM To: Lobo Subject: Its Christmas time :) Hey Lobo Marry Christmas
